# 🎯 Windsurf AI Rules - Dynamic Brand Configuration

## CRITICAL: Project Context
**BEFORE ANYTHING ELSE, read `.claude/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`**

This is a **customizable boilerplate template**. Each customer will have:
- Different project name (NOT "PropelKit" or "Acme SaaS")
- Different branding, URLs, emails
- All configured in `src/config/brand.ts`

**NEVER hardcode "PropelKit" or "Acme SaaS" in generated code!**

