## 🚨 Next.js 15 Breaking Change

**Route params are NOW Promises:**

```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT - Next.js 15
export async function GET(
  request: NextRequest,
  { params }: { params: Promise<{ id: string }> }
) {
  const { id } = await params; // MUST await
}

// ❌ WRONG - Will break!
export async function GET(
  request: NextRequest,
  { params }: { params: { id: string } }
) {
  const id = params.id; // No await
}
```

