## Dynamic Brand Configuration

**ALWAYS import and use brand config:**

```typescript
import { brand } from '@/config/brand';

// ✅ CORRECT - Dynamic
const title = `Welcome to ${brand.name}`;
const email = brand.email.fromSupport;
