```

### GST Calculation (18%)
```typescript
const gstAmount = baseAmount * 0.18;
const total = baseAmount + gstAmount;

// Split for intra-state
const cgst = gstAmount / 2;
const sgst = gstAmount / 2;

// Or inter-state
const igst = gstAmount;
```

### Phone Validation
```typescript
